title: Boards Level 5?
body:
I was just curious on how to level up on this. I am kind of a noob when it comes to the boards. This is apparently the only place I can post but any help would be appreciated.



Thanks{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}

replies.body: It looks like you have leveled up now!  It can take a moment for the boards profile to sync up.  Looks good!
